\c 137
\s Ukukhala kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli abathunjiweyo
\p
\v 1 Emifuleni yeBhabhiloni sahlala phansi khona, yebo sakhala inyembezi, lapho sikhumbula iZiyoni.
\v 2 Amachacho ethu sawaphanyeka eminyezaneni phakathi kwayo\x + Jobe 40.22.\x*.
\v 3 Ngoba khonapho abasithumbayo basicela amazwi engoma, labasimotshayo \add bacela\add* injabulo \add besithi\add*: Sihlabeleleni \add enye\add* yezingoma zeZiyoni.
\p
\v 4 Singahlabela njani ingoma yeN\nd kosi\nd* elizweni lemzini\x + Neh. 2.3.\x*?
\v 5 Uba ngikukhohlwa, Jerusalema, isandla sami sokunene kasikhohlwe \add ubungcitshi\x + Hlab. 76.5.\x*\add*.
\v 6 Ulimi lwami kalunamathele elwangeni lwami, uba ngingakukhumbuli, uba ngingaphakamisi iJerusalema phezu kwentokozo yami enkulu\x + Jobe 29.10.\x*.
\v 7 Khumbula, N\nd kosi\nd*, ngabantwana bakoEdoma, \add ngo\add*suku lweJerusalema, abathi: Dilizani, dilizani\f + \fk dilizani: \fl Heb. \fq embulani.\f*, kuze kube sesisekelweni sayo\x + Jer. 49.7-22. Lilo 4.21,22. Hez. 25.12-14. 35.5. Obad. 10-14. Amos 1.11.\x*.
\v 8 Ndodakazi yeBhabhiloni, ozabhujiswa\x + Isa. 13.1-14,23. 47.1-15. Jer. 25.12. 50.1-46.\x*, ubusisiwe ozaphindisela kuwe izenzo ozenze kithi\x + Jer. 50.15,29. Isam. 18.6.\x*\x + Jer. 51.24.\x*.
\v 9 Ubusisiwe ozabamba asakaze abantwana bakho edwaleni\x + 2 Kho. 8.12.\x*.
